<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٨ -<span class="c5"> بَاب:</span> مَا قِيلَ فِي الصَّوَّاغِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَقَالَ طَاوُسٌ،<span class="c5"> عَنِ ابْنِ عَبَّاسٍ <span class="special">﵄</span>:</span> قَالَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>: <span class="c2">(لَا يُخْتَلَى خَلَاهَا)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ الْعَبَّاسُ:</span> إِلَّا الْإِذْخِرَ، فَإِنَّهُ لِقَيْنِهِمْ وَبُيُوتِهِمْ،<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">(إِلَّا الْإِذْخِرَ)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
